## Method Extraction Sequence

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Main as Main Method
    participant H1 as Helper 1: ShouldSkip
    participant H2 as Helper 2: IsOrderCancellable
    participant H3 as Helper 3: CleanupStale
    participant H4 as Helper 4: CreateSpec
    
    Dev->>H2: 1. Extract IsOrderCancellable (CYC 2)
    Note over H2: Reusable validation logic
    
    Dev->>H3: 2. Extract CleanupStaleFollowerTarget (CYC 3)
    H3->>H2: Uses IsOrderCancellable
    
    Dev->>H1: 3. Extract ShouldSkipTargetReplacement (CYC 3)
    H1->>H3: Uses CleanupStaleFollowerTarget
    
    Dev->>H4: 4. Extract CreateFollowerTargetReplaceSpec (CYC 4)
    Note over H4: FSM spec builder
    
    Dev->>Main: 5. Refactor Main Method (CYC 5)
    Main->>H1: Calls ShouldSkip
    Main->>H2: Calls IsOrderCancellable
    Main->>H4: Calls CreateSpec
```

