## Decision Tree Before Extraction

```mermaid
graph TD
    Start[Start] --> G1{ExecutingAccount<br/>null?}
    G1 -->|Yes| End1[Return]
    G1 -->|No| G2{isFilled OR<br/>isRunner OR<br/>qty <= 0?}
    
    G2 -->|Yes| G3{Stale target<br/>exists?}
    G3 -->|Yes| G4{Order<br/>cancellable?}
    G4 -->|Yes| Cancel1[Cancel Order]
    G4 -->|No| Remove1[Remove from dict]
    Cancel1 --> Remove1
    G3 -->|No| End2[Return]
    Remove1 --> End2
    
    G2 -->|No| G5{Old target<br/>exists?}
    G5 -->|No| End3[Return]
    G5 -->|Yes| G6{Order<br/>cancellable?}
    G6 -->|No| End4[Return]
    G6 -->|Yes| G7{newPrice > 0?}
    G7 -->|No| End5[Return]
    G7 -->|Yes| Build[Build FSM Spec]
    Build --> Stamp[Stamp Grace]
    Stamp --> Cancel2[Cancel Order]
    Cancel2 --> End6[Return]
    
    style G1 fill:#ffd43b
    style G2 fill:#ffd43b
    style G3 fill:#ffd43b
    style G4 fill:#ffd43b
    style G5 fill:#ffd43b
    style G6 fill:#ffd43b
    style G7 fill:#ffd43b
```

## Decision Tree After Extraction

```mermaid
graph TD
    Start[Start] --> G1{ExecutingAccount<br/>null?}
    G1 -->|Yes| End1[Return]
    G1 -->|No| Skip[ShouldSkipTargetReplacement]
    
